  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM17">
<l>aṉpā laṭaivatev vāṟukoṉ mēlatō rāṭaravan</l>
<l>taṉpā loruvaraic cāravoṭ ṭātatu vēyumaṉṟi</l>
<l>muṉpā yiṉatalai yōṭukaḷ kōttavai yārttuveḷḷai</l>
<l>yeṉpā yiṉavu maṇintaṅkō rēṟukan tēṟuvatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In which way is there nearing [him] with love? A dancing snake that is on [him]</l>
<l>does not agree to anyone nearing him. Even apart from that,</l>
<l>as strung shells from heads, that were earlier , rattle and as</l>
<l>what are white bones adorn [him] there he joyfully mounts a bull.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
